    <deploymentStatus>Deployed</deploymentStatus>
    <description>One row per (LoggerNotificationMatch__c, LoggerNotificationRecipient__c) tuple - so a match with N recipients produces N delivery rows. The denormalized LoggerNotificationService__c lookup is copied from the recipient at write time so the service record page can show a Deliveries related list directly. Powers per-recipient dispatch tracking and is the natural home for future delivery-status fields (attempt count, last error, retry state).</description>
